# Code Owners for app-accounting-modular Repository

# This file defines who owns what code and who should review changes

# Format: path pattern @owner1 @owner2

# Global owners (fallback for all files)

* @modular-accounting/maintainers

# Repository-specific ownership rules

/docs/ @modular-accounting/docs
/.github/ @modular-accounting/platform
/apps/ @modular-accounting/backend
/cli/ @modular-accounting/backend
/plugins/ @modular-accounting/backend

