*.pem @Nobodyworld/security-team
*.key @Nobodyworld/security-team
*secret* @Nobodyworld/security-team
*.env* @Nobodyworld/security-team

# CI/CD files (standard organization rules)

.github/workflows/ @Nobodyworld/devops-team
.github/actions/ @Nobodyworld/devops-team

# Package management files (standard organization rules)

package.json @Nobodyworld/frontend-team
